high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table in front of and left of the fridge.
Grab a dirty bowl from the table.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the bowl in the sink, wash it, then fill it with water and grab it.
Walk to the kitchen shelf on the left.
Place the bowl of water in the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Clean a bowl and fill it with water to display on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk right, veering right to the kitchen table.
Pick up the clear bowl on the table.
Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Wash the bowl in the sink.
Turn left and veer left to the corner of the room with the shelves in it.
Place the bowl on the second to the bottom shelf, to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bowl on a shelf.

high_descs: Wash the bowl in the sink
Place the bowl on a shelf
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned bowl on a shelf
